Sample images attribution and license
======================================

The following files in this directory contain frames from the
"Drone Dataset (UAV)" by Mehdi Özel, overlaid with this project's own
detection outputs (bounding boxes / labels):

  - val_predictions.jpg
  - rknn_sim_detection.jpg

The underlying photographs are part of the Drone Dataset (UAV) and are
distributed under the MIT License (reproduced below). The bounding-box
overlays are produced by this project.

Dataset source:
  https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/dasmehdixtr/drone-dataset-uav?select=drone_dataset_yolo

